@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(0.89)
    v0 = wp.sin(0.87)
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.85 + v1 + 0.84)) - wp.cos(v0))
    tmp = v1
    tmp = 0.53
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.27) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.94)) / v0)
    v0 = ((0.32 * (v1 + 0.05 * tmp + 0.23)) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.56) + (v1 + 0.77 + tmp + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
